PoleTarget: # Transform to use as the pole target(specifies the plane of solution)
Spin: Float: Spin(Default : 0.0) # Amount of twist to apply to the solution plane(Additive after application of Pole Target motion)
EndEffector: # Transform to use as the end effector of the IK system
StartJointFKTransform:
Transform : Start Joint FK Transform         # Transform for the Start Joint when in FK mode
Transform: Mid Joint FK Transform           # Transform for the Mid Joint when in FK mode
Transform : End Joint FK Transform          # Transform for the End Joint when in FK mode
